[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This said spirit was not given <qex>alonely</qex> unto him, but
unto all his heirs and posterity.</q> <rj><qau>Latimer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

